  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880310/extras/d497a9a7d4627080a04e225dea82b648.avif?t=1745320815\" width=555 height=312 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dreamlike horror visual novel, heavy on atmosphere and open to interpretation. Go in with an open mind and come out with an extra head. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30-60 minutes gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Creepy story and music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden scenes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two Endings</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Best experienced with headphones.</i><u> </u></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2880310/extras/d497a9a7d4627080a04e225dea82b648.avif?t=1745320815\" width=555 height=312 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dreamlike horror visual novel, heavy on atmosphere and open to interpretation. Go in with an open mind and come out with an extra head. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30-60 minutes gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Creepy story and music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden scenes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two Endings</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Best experienced with headphones.</i><u> </u></p>",
